# Package Manager Standard

- Use `pnpm` for installs, adds, and scripts.
- Do not use `npm` or `npx`.

## Examples

```bash
# ✅ GOOD
pnpm install
pnpm add package-name
pnpm run dev
pnpm dlx some-cli

# ❌ BAD
npm install
npm add package-name
npm run dev
npx some-cli
```
